      "description": "<div class=\"Section0\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID:15.6pt none\"><h4 style=\"MARGIN:2pt 0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><strong>恍惚</strong></h4><p class=\"26\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM:0pt;MARGIN-TOP:0pt;LINE-HEIGHT:13pt;MARGIN-RIGHT:0pt;TEXT-INDENT:12pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-char-indent-count:1.0000;mso-add-space:auto;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\">·恍惚的生物不能執行反應。</p><p class=\"26\" style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM:0pt;MARGIN-TOP:0pt;LINE-HEIGHT:13pt;MARGIN-RIGHT:0pt;TEXT-INDENT:12pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-char-indent-count:1.0000;mso-add-space:auto;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\">·恍惚的生物在自己的回合內，只能從動作、附贈動作、消耗移動力三種行為中選擇一項執行。</p></div>",
